org.universAAL.middleware.managers.distributedmw.api

Interface DistributedBusMemberListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BusMemberMonitor

    public interface DistributedBusMemberListener
    Interface of BusMember registry listener. If registered at the service IBusMemberRegistry it gets notified if any changes occurs in it.
    Author:
    Carsten Stockloew

      • busMemberAdded

        void busMemberAdded(PeerCard origin,
                    String busMemberID,
                    String busName,
                    BusMemberType memberType,

        Invoked when a new BusMember is registered in the bus.

      • busMemberRemoved

        void busMemberRemoved(PeerCard origin,
                      String busMemberID)
        Invoked when an existing BusMember is unregistered from the bus.
        Parameters:
        origin - the peer on which the event occurred.
        member - removed bus member
        type - type of bus IBusMemberRegistry

      • regParamsAdded

        void regParamsAdded(PeerCard origin,
                    String busMemberID,
                    Resource[] params)
        Invoked when registration parameters of an existing BusMember are added. Registration parameters can be, for example, ServiceProfiles for ServiceCallees or ContextEventPattern for ContextSubscriber.
        Parameters:
        origin - the peer on which the event occurred.
        busMemberID - the ID of the bus member for which the registration parameters have been added.
        params - the registration parameters that have been added.

      • regParamsRemoved

        void regParamsRemoved(PeerCard origin,
                      String busMemberID,
                      Resource[] params)
        Invoked when registration parameters of an existing BusMember are removed. Registration parameters can be, for example, ServiceProfiles for ServiceCallees or ContextEventPattern for ContextSubscriber.
        Parameters:
        origin - the peer on which the event occurred.
        busMemberID - the ID of the bus member for which the registration parameters have been removed.
        params - the registration parameters that have been removed.
